{"name":"Avatar of Skeletron","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"Patron, God of Death, Balance","alignment":"Lawful Good","hitDice":"30","armorName":"natural armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":11,"otherArmorDesc":"25 (","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"22 (5d8)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"16","dexPoints":"8","conPoints":"20","intPoints":"18","wisPoints":"24","chaPoints":"16","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"120","telepathy":0,"cr":"7","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":true,"legendariesDescription":"[MON] can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Legendary Resistance","desc":"[MON] can use its legendary actions to reroll saving throws that it failed."},{"name":"Divine Wrath","desc":"[MON] channels powers from all the effigy souls as the God of the Dead. [MON] starts with 5 soul force."}],"actions":[{"name":"Spirit Leap","desc":"[MON] sends a spirit companion to strike at a creature it can see. [WIS ATK] to hit. _Hit:_ [WIS 2D6] necrotic damage. [MON] gains 1 soul force."},{"name":"Judgement Day","desc":"[MON] expends 5 soul force to send a creature to the City of the Dead. A creature [MON] sees takes [10d10] necrotic damage (halved if they succeed a **DC [WIS SAVE]** Con Save). A creature that is downed due to this attack instantly dies."},{"name":"Ember","desc":"[MON] expends 1 soul force to light a creature up with soul fire. [WIS ATK] to hit, but this ignore armor. _Hit_: [WIS 3d6] necrotic damage."},{"name":"Repel","desc":"[MON] expends 1 Soul Force to unleash a necrotic blast that knocks all creatures prone and back 30ft if they fail a **DC [WIS SAVE]** strength save."},{"name":"Wither","desc":"[MON] expends 1 Soul Force to cause a creature to Wither away. It must make a **DC [WIS SAVE] Cha Save** or take [3d6] necrotic damage. In addition, their stats all decrease by 2 for the next minute."},{"name":"Soul Barrier","desc":"[MON] consumes 2 Soul Force to form a protective barrier. [MON] gains 20 temp HP and 2 AC until the barrier is destroyed."},{"name":"Soulbind","desc":"[MON] expends 2 Soul Force to bind a creature's soul. It must make a **DC [WIS SAVE]** Con Save or take [3d6] necrotic damage and get slowed for the next minute."},{"name":"Overload","desc":"[MON] expends 3 Soul Force to unleash a 30ft. necrotic blast. All creatures within the range take [8d6] necrotic damage, halved if they make a **DC [WIS SAVE]** Dex Save."},{"name":"Life Drain","desc":"[MON] expends 3 soul force to drain the life out of all creatures it can see. All creatures transfer [1d20] HP to the Skeletron."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[{"name":"Spirit Sceptre","desc":"[MON] makes a Spirit Leap attack."},{"name":"Soul Harvest","desc":"All creatures [MON] can see must make a **DC [WIS SAVE]** Charisma Save or lose [1d6] max HP. [MON] gains 1 soul force for every creature that failed the save."},{"name":"Toll the Dead","desc":"[MON] rings a bell of impending doom. A creature [MON] can see must make a **DC [WIS SAVE]** Wisdom Save or take [2d12 - 1] necrotic damage (or [2d8] if at max health). In addition, [MON] gains a Soul Force."},{"name":"Dark Souls","desc":"[MON] can take any action if it spends double the Soul Force cost."}],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"con","order":2},{"name":"wis","order":4}],"skills":[{"name":"history","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"insight","stat":"wis"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"religion","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"}],"damagetypes":[{"name":"necrotic","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"},{"name":"radiant","note":" (Vulnerable)","type":"v"}],"specialdamage":[{"name":"bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing from nonmagical attacks","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"}],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Skeletron","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":4,"damage":[]}